These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, milk, mirinda, tea
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, green, orange, brown
4 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, dog, frog
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, ship, tram, van
 1. the person who likes green is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
 2. the person drinking milk is the person who likes brown##1
 3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person who likes orange is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
 7. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 8. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left##1
10. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
11. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |      3      |   4   |
| Beverage    | mirinda   | milk       | almond-milk | tea   |
| Color        | green    | brown  | orange      | lilac |
| Pet         | frog      | chinchilla | dog         | cat   |
| Transport   | quad-bike | ship       | tram        | van   |

