.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-3::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: green, orange, pink, black
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, gospel, indie, rock
4 different pets are kept: cat, dog, hedgehog, turtle
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, cycling, ice-hockey, volleyball
 1. the fan of indie is the person who likes pink##1
 2. the fan of folk is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person who likes black is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
 4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 5. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the fan of rock##1
 6. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
 7. the fan of folk is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 8. the owner of the cat is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the fan of gospel##2
 9. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who likes green##1
10. the person who likes orange is on the left or right of the person who likes black##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |     4      |
| Color          | orange | black  | green | pink      |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | rock    | gospel      | indie      |
| Pet           | turtle     | cat     | dog         | hedgehog   |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | cricket | cycling     | volleyball |

