.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-20::.
4 different games are played: canasta, snooker, mah-jongg, backgammon
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, dancer, mechanic, scientist
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, mystery, satire
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, snowboarding, soccer, swimming
 1. the person playing canasta is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the analyst##1
 3. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
 4. the dancer is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2
 5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
 6. the person watching adventure movies is between the dancer and the person who's sport is skiing##2
 7. the person watching mystery movies is the scientist##1
 8. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
 9. the person playing mah-jongg is the dancer##1
10. the person watching adventure movies is the mechanic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3     |     4     |
| Game          | snooker | backgammon   | mah-jongg   | canasta |
| Job           | analyst   | mechanic     | dancer   | scientist |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | adventure    | satire   | mystery   |
| Sport         | skiing    | snowboarding | swimming | soccer    |

 